# Raspberry Pi Pico / MicroPython patterns
CRITICAL  PANIC           PANIC:
HIGH      HARD_FAULT      HardFault
HIGH      ASSERT          AssertionError
HIGH      MEM_ERROR       MemoryError
HIGH      IMPORT_ERROR    ImportError
HIGH      WDT_RESET       Watchdog Reset
WARN      TRACEBACK       Traceback .most recent call last.
WARN      EXCEPTION       Exception:
INFO      SOFT_REBOOT     MPY: soft reboot
